<section>
  <p>
    Richard Caballero is a Group Product Design Manager at Esri, where he leads
    design across ArcGIS product areas spanning professional GIS, indoors,
    enterprise management, graph data, and intelligence. His work connects
    design, engineering, and product strategy across web, desktop, and mobile
    products.
  </p>
  <p>
    Richard's academic background bridges human cognition and computational
    systems. He earned a B.S. in Cognitive Neuroscience from UC San Diego in
    2010, and later completed an M.S. in Data Science and GIS from Claremont
    Graduate University in 2023, where he was awarded the Esri Fellowship.
  </p>
  <p>
    His current focus includes scaling design leadership across ArcGIS products,
    integrating AI into professional GIS workflows, advancing cross-platform
    design systems, and shaping graph and intelligence experiences through
    strong product and engineering alignment.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Talks</h2>
  <ul class="list">
    {% for talk in links.talks %}
      <li>
        <article>
          <h3><a href="{{ talk.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ talk.title }}</a></h3>
          <p class="meta">{{ talk.event }} · {{ talk.date | formatDate }}{% if talk.location %} · {{ talk.location }}{% endif %}</p>
        </article>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Publications</h2>
  <ul class="list">
    {% for publication in links.publications %}
      <li>
        <article>
          <h3><a href="{{ publication.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ publication.title }}</a></h3>
          <p class="meta">{{ publication.venue }} · {{ publication.date | formatDate }}</p>
        </article>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Mentions</h2>
  <ul class="list">
    {% for mention in links.mentions %}
      <li>
        <article>
          <h3><a href="{{ mention.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{{ mention.title }}</a></h3>
          <p class="meta">{{ mention.publication }} · {{ mention.date | formatDate }}{% if mention.author %} · {{ mention.author }}{% endif %}</p>
        </article>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
